  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3053500/extras/7712519f77f6c2107a06b948c1700c93.webp?t=1743544621\" width=616 height=38 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3053500/extras/332d5e159e2896f5baa8151cdfc5775a.poster.avif?t=1743544621\" width=600 height=260 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3053500/extras/332d5e159e2896f5baa8151cdfc5775a.webm?t=1743544621\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3053500/extras/332d5e159e2896f5baa8151cdfc5775a.mp4?t=1743544621\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Explore a dark, seemingly abandoned mall with a shopping list of items you want to collect. <br>However, you'll be chased by Jeff, the night-shift janitor.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3053500/extras/05f6865d16caf2178658375d903ed531.webp?t=1743544621\" width=616 height=38 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3053500/extras/40d86a1b36f8a5fbecf603b12113a0fd.poster.avif?t=1743544621\" width=600 height=260 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3053500/extras/40d86a1b36f8a5fbecf603b12113a0fd.webm?t=1743544621\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3053500/extras/40d86a1b36f8a5fbecf603b12113a0fd.mp4?t=1743544621\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Find keys and other crucial items to unlock doors and access hidden areas,<br>allowing you to delve deeper into the mall.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3053500/extras/aeb12f8e6a9789be9eea3a8da21e7d8f.webp?t=1743544621\" width=616 height=38 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3053500/extras/c2e66e3c28503bb8b4f90e3a6d446387.poster.avif?t=1743544621\" width=600 height=260 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3053500/extras/c2e66e3c28503bb8b4f90e3a6d446387.webm?t=1743544621\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3053500/extras/c2e66e3c28503bb8b4f90e3a6d446387.mp4?t=1743544621\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>If Jeff catches you, it's game over! Stay alert to avoid getting caught.<br>Hide, run, and outsmart Jeff to survive and complete your mission.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3053500/extras/845c80df4d5a43a590a0d5a84437b9eb.webp?t=1743544621\" width=616 height=38 /></span><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>1-5 Player Co-Op<br></li><li>Voice Chat<br></li><li>Multiple Maps<br></li><li>Unlockable Skins<br></li><li>Scaling Difficulty<br></li><li>Jeff</li></ul>",
